The paper discusses the robustness of decision tree learning algorithms, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also presents theoretical analysis and sample complexity results, which are related to data mining (cs.DM). Additionally, decision trees are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SI) applications.
